	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Literas tuas, chare frater, copiose scriptas de motibus istis vestris <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648" cert="high">Rheticis</placeName> tardius accepi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scriptae erant 10. februarii; recepi illas 20. eiusdem mensis, sed videram prius eas, quas scripseras ad <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p252" cert="high">I[oachimum] Beldium</persName>; has enim mihi exhibuit interpres legati regis, qui <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Saloduri</placeName> agit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ille fuerat <placeName ref="l646" cert="high">Claronae</placeName>, per nos redibat <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760" cert="high">Salodurum</placeName> et hic me salutabat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Proinde totam historiam exponendam putavi consulibus, id quod feci.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Simul afferuntur <placeName ref="l300" cert="high">Lucerna</placeName> literae testificantes et ipsae cieri apud vos seditiones.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Indigne ferebant nostri, quod citius periculum vestrum exposuissetis <placeName ref="l300" cert="high">Lucernatibus</placeName> quam nobis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nihilominus conscripsere nostri commitia<note type="misc">... mitia</note> Badae 4. martii celebranda, in quibus consultetur de remedio turbis illis adhibendo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Simul misere nostri cursorem cum literis ad vestros perquisitum, ut res habeant vestrae, et significatum propter vos <persName type="auto_name">Rhetos</persName> conscripta esse comitia <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l21">Badam</placeName> etc.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Haec iam antea haud dubie nosti.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Valde doleo propter principes exteros et studiis partium sic nos discindi per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetiam</placeName>; laceratio haec certissimum est prognosticon res nostras brevi corruituras.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="auto_name">Locarnas</persName> quidam rediens pridie <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolano</placeName> significat navibus iustum allatum <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanorum</placeName> militum exercitum Ianuam, qui per hyperna sit disponendus per <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l736" cert="high">Pedemontium</placeName> et <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l306" cert="high">Mediolanum</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid hoc, si vera sunt, quae ille refert?</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Addit ille <persName type="auto_name">Sanpetrium</persName> iam totam occupasse <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2801" cert="high">Corsicam</placeName> uno aut altero loco excepto; classem quoque a <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l2510" cert="high">Turca</placeName> instrui.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">De morte <persName ref="p18556" cert="high">Maximiliani</persName> nihildum accepi.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Diu iam expecto literas ex <placeName ref="l361" cert="high">Neroberga</placeName> et <placeName ref="l18" cert="high">Augusta Vindelicorum</placeName>; alioqui ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germania</placeName> iam septimanas aliquot nihil habeo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Quae fuse ad me perscripta sunt ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l869">Transylvaniae</placeName> confinis, in summam collecta et descripta hic mitto, sed ut per proximum nuncium remittas; communica cum amplissimo d. legato, quem honorificentissime ex me salutabis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Legatus regis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l760">Salodorensis</placeName> dicitur descendisse <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileam</placeName>, quod magna ibi sint impedimenta foederis pangendi, quae ille amoliri conetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Nescio, an <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernates</placeName> receperint.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Diu nihil accipio literarum vel ex <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Berna</placeName> vel <placeName ref="l167" cert="high">Geneva</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tu si quid certi habes ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l834" cert="high">Italia</placeName>, communica.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="22" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ad tuam querelam nihil respondere possum, quam quod ego in paribus casibus facio, id ipsum te doceo: respicere in deum, illum invocare et perstare in officio.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="23" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale aeternum.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="24" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Februarii 23. 1565.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="25" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus qui semper.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="26" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Saluta consules et viros bonos.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="27" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Praestantissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8009" cert="high">Ioanni Fabritio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae fideli ministro, domino meo colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="28" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l98" cert="high">Chur</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
